{
  "stem": "1413.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not three years, two years and a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Work.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a foreman again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Doing what, very good question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more than two years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But let me tell you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before I bragged-- or you can call it bragging-- that I was always a good worker, I was even such a good worker that is unbelievable to people who were in the camp who can only imagine what it was.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The maestra, they called it, he gave me his bicycle to do the chores, what I had to do, and what I did do.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's indescribable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It takes maybe 20 videos if I tell you what I did, because I'm an active person, what I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even so much, that if the German knows what I did to sabotage them, they might start a war just to get a hold of me, and to kill me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I delivered the goods.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What the maestra want, the boss wants, he got delivered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I did, I did transportation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to pick, for instance, a pipe here, bring it over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had to be sawed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I had the other pipe that's connecting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all-- they build it-- they build it to make synthetic material for the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was so taken in with me that in wintertime, we couldn't do as much work because in Poland this can be pretty cold.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That he, I can't say it in English-- maybe, it explains it better in German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He protected us in wintertime, only to keep the same people to do work for him again when summer came-- that he even sabotaged the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
